果：<br />\n<br />\n1。此舉將有力地促使黃周等人進入全世界最年輕的諾貝爾奬得主行列；<br />\n<br />\n2。港人不會因此退卻，相反，會因此被激怒。更大規模的抗爭會讓中共陷入更大的困境；<br />\n<br />\n3。美國的「香港人權與民主法案」百分百會通過。<br />\n<br />\n（順便小爆料：一個大規模的致美國國會的公開信很快就會公布，數以百計的連署者以美國政界，學界和人權團體的領軍人物為主，也包括中國海外民運人士，我已經簽署。我們將針對香港問題提出空前強烈的要求。）<br />\n<br />\n中國要瘋狂，我們攔不住；但是，我們一定會讓他們付出無比沈重的代價。<br />\n<br />\n那或許會成為一個歷史大轉型的契機也說不定。只是港人會為此付出代價，令人痛惜。"},{"pid":"071526a2470adb0be58cbf13c4feca8db2dea0a9","tid":1518081,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c95a5198df3fd6692cf77d6a2acaa897d454938","tid":1518081,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faaad756caa0f5af3e88a9802b325e079a7bf4a","tid":1518081,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUig8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=33d1c5c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUig8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=5ad1906c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUig8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=add17da9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"琴日睇得多超快速<br />\n今日睇野開始慢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"帶你個衰仔睇醫生， 又乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a124a2a9f97e1684865809e9eb2f